取更大權益<br />\n4. 聯合其他SEN家長, 搵教育局幫, 可以要指名要教育心理學家出面搞, 呢班人做既野就係迫學校做野+ 撥錢. 家長記得要準備好相關既醫療報告<br />\n<br />\n總結就係搵警方同教育局雙重施壓, 記住唔好覺得唔好意思, 呢啲全部都係你個仔所應得既權利同待遇黎, 家長唔行前一步, 就好難再進一步幫你個仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n道理同爭取民主自由差唔多, 你唔出聲唔行前一步,人地自然當你無到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd35fe9f178ba2c56879ad8646e1697b0f83ae9","tid":179139,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾學校垃圾校長，死咗佢咪為禍人間啦"},{"pid":"1da8bc7a14422d7cc9ab916790ed2b79698881ab","tid":179139,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"係咪天水圍十八鄉小學"},{"pid":"42f9fa977ee21247cd4a56f81e876011162cd7de","tid":179139,"uid":1219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f387acff87d4842e2936029f0a2c32ca5a6670","tid":179139,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"小學都比人屈過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人調位調左去角落頭，附近d人又調走哂，個陣真係講乜都冇人信。老豆老母都唔撚信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人屈左d乜已經唔記得左，不過細細個就知道人情冷暖其實都幾好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25672ecab89a62734db19590e0aa222e7d559d9","tid":179139,"uid":84,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092d888aca066bd5de00aee387a1d0e954f978fa","tid":179139,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T09:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學都比人屈過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人調位調左去角落頭，附近d人又調走哂，個陣真係講乜都冇人信。老豆老母都唔撚信我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人屈左d乜已經唔記得左，不過細細個就知道人情冷暖其實都幾好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD老師嘅懲罰方式真係好on9 以前都俾老師調撚過去角落住勁撚有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}